```

### ğŸ§ª Manual Setup:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/12bucks.git
cd 12bucks
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
```

